latestIgtvVideos.caption:
💜🤩 If you have been looking for a styler that gets close, really close to each strand of hair while styling, then this is the right tool for you.
@alantrumanofficial ‘s Float Styler helps get the job done in less time due to more contact with the hair.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ 
📌What is it actually?
A hair straightener in which plates are not fitted into the body but are air-suspended on a silicon holder.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ 
📌How does the suspended plates technology help?
Unlike standard straighteners, the suspended plates perfectly align with your hair to capture each strand in one stroke, helping you achieve one-pass perfection with a product that glides smoothly from root to tip.
  ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ 
📌What is the cool-touch technology all about?
The innovative suspended plates provide cool touch technology by directing the heat away from the outer casing. Grip the top of the straightener for ultimate control and ease, whether you’re creating straight styles, curls or waves.

Grab this innovative beauty at an amazing discount exclusively on @mynykaa 💯🔥
